For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Cosmoem (TCG Pocket).

Cosmoem has been featured on 4 different cards since it debuted in the Sun & Moon expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Cosmoem cards are normally Psychic-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Cosmoem

Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
